== Configuration
	 The following will create a connection for an embedded Derby.
	
	 Define the driver for the derby access. Go to Window->
		Preferences and select "Data Management" -> Connectivity -> Driver
		Definition. Press Add. Select Derby and the version you want to use.
		If your Derby version is not listed selected the highest number
		displayed.
	
	
image::dtpconfig10.gif[]
				
			
		
	

	Select then the tab jar press _Add..._ and select the derby.jar from
		your project folder "lib".
	
